0:
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: 92.7 WOBM News Flash Briefing brings you the latest news from Ocean County – headlines from your community about politics, crime, events, and the stories from your own backyard. Want to know more? Listen now and read the latest at WOBM.com and on the 92.7 WOBM app.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
